text.tspan: Have you ever had a business idea but couldn’t realize it
due to technical limitations and cost limitations?
Unlike other funding platforms that fund real products,
I’con share your entrepreneurial ‘idea’ with explanations,
designs, etc. I’con is a platform that gives an opportunity to
entrepreneurs who have difficulties in starting a real business
can meet technicians with production capabilities,
legal experts who can provide legal advice,
planners who can improve ideas for the better.
Share your infinite ideas and dreams in I’con!
